txt.en: Spiders skitter about Dâr Matum, silent despite their size. They appear to be hunting the local fauna to grow their numbers. It is only a matter of time before they chance attacking a traveller on the road. For the safety of Gondor, they cannot be ignored.
You have defeated many spiders in Dâr Matum.
Spiders have inhabited the ruins of Dâr Matum.
You have defeated many spiders in Dâr Matum, making it safer for all who travel between Ringló Vale and Lamedon.
